WEBVTT

00:04:58.151 --> 00:05:00.451
ni muhimu kama kile wasichosema.

00:05:01.766 --> 00:05:03.480
Kwa hiyo namna gani --

00:05:04.472 --> 00:05:07.560
Najifunzaje kuwa na maarifa ya uono?

00:05:08.384 --> 00:05:10.661
Inaelezewa na kama nne.

00:05:10.685 --> 00:05:13.167
Kila hali mpya, kila tatizo jipya --

00:05:13.191 --> 00:05:14.725
huwa tunafanyia kazi kama nne.

00:05:14.749 --> 00:05:16.238
Kwanza, tunatathmini hali yetu.

00:05:16.262 --> 00:05:18.497
Tunauliza, " Ni kipi tulichonacho mbele
yetu?"

00:05:18.521 --> 00:05:20.059
Kisha, tunakichambua.

00:05:20.083 --> 00:05:21.408
Tunasema, "Kipi ni muhimu?

00:05:21.432 --> 00:05:23.164
Nahitaji nini? Kipi sihitaji?"

00:05:23.188 --> 00:05:26.954
Kisha, tunakiunda katika maongezi, katika
kumbukumbu, maandishi, barua pepe.

00:05:26.978 --> 00:05:29.577
Na kisha, tunatenda: tunafanya maamuzi.